title: Nightmare on Elm Street (collected)
description:
A collection from all over the place of Freddy comics, not sure where I got them from so sorry if anyone doesn't get credit where it's deserved. I've been getting what I can for years but don't think I've found all of them yet. I'll be adding more if and when I can get more. This collects some of Marvels, Innovations, Avatar and Wildstorms books. Most of it is in Jpeg format.

For more info: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Nightmare_on_Elm_Street_%28comics%29

Files: 

Art: 

Marvel, Innovation and Wildstorm. Mostly covers from the series but also includes FvsJvsA extras.

Books: 
Marvel: 
Nightmare on Elm Street Books 1 and 2.

Innovation: 
Freddy's Dead comic series 1-3 + bonus
Nightmares on Elm Street 1-6
A Nightmare on Elm Street: The Beginning 1-2 + Scripts for 1-3 + plot This was canceled after the second issue.

Avatar: House of Horror books
A Nightmare on Elm Street: Special
A Nightmare on Elm Street: Paranoid
A Nightmare on Elm Street: Fearbook

Wildstorm:
A Nightmare on Elm Street: 1-8
New Line Cinema's House Of Horror: Includes a Texas Chainsaw story
Freddy vs. Jason vs. Ash
Freddy vs. Jason vs. Ash - Nightmare Warriors

First Upload so if I messed up let me know.
